overview: This live performance video features the Irish-American band who specialize in performing the traditional music of their ancestral land. Filmed at a 1998 concert in Burlington, Vermont, the video features classic tracks like "Big Reel of Ballynacally" and "She Is Like The Swallow." The talented performers play their Celtic instruments--the flute and the fiddler -- with awe- inspiring skill.
title: Solas Live
